---
title: Smoky Lentil Salad with Za'atar-Spiced Crisps and Zesty Garlic Sauce
description: This hearty, plant-focused lentil salad is packed with texture, flavours and a healthy dose of veggies all at once! The za'atar-spiced flatbread crisps bulk out this already bountiful plate and add a pleasantly earthy crunch!
